<script type='text/javascript'>
    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function () {
        $(document).ready(function() {
            var $findEyeMdDivs = $('.uber-findeyemd');

            $findEyeMdDivs.each(function(i, element) {
                var $div = $(element);

                var $oldzip = $div.find('input.form-control');
                var $zip = $oldzip.clone();
                $oldzip.replaceWith( $zip);
                
                var $oldbtn = $div.find('button.btn-eyemd');
                var $btn = $oldbtn.clone();
                $oldbtn.replaceWith($btn);

                var newClick = function() {
                    window.zip = $zip[0];
                    goFindAnEyeMd();
                };

                $btn.click(newClick);
                $zip.keydown(function(event) {
                    if (event.which == 13) {
                        event.preventDefault();
                        $btn.click();
                    }
                });
            });
            
            
        });
    }, false);
    
</script>
